#: ../../../project/changelog.md:1177
msgid ""
"{{ Fix }} `getattr(jsproxy, 'python_reserved_word')` works as expected again "
"(as well as `hasattr` and `setattr`). This fixes a regression introduced in "
"{pr}`3617`. {pr}`3926`"
