#: ../../../project/changelog.md:2153
msgid ""
"New packages: opencv-python {pr}`2305`, ffmpeg {pr}`2305`, libwebp {pr}"
"`2305`, h5py, pkgconfig and libhdf5 {pr}`2411`, bitarray {pr}`2459`, gsw {pr}"
"`2511`, cftime {pr}`2504`, svgwrite, jsonschema, tskit {pr}`2506`, xarray "
"{pr}`2538`, demes, libgsl, newick, ruamel, msprime {pr}`2548`, gmpy2 {pr}"
"`2665`, xgboost {pr}`2537`, galpy {pr}`2676`, shapely, geos {pr}`2725`, "
"suitesparse, sparseqr {pr}`2685`, libtiff {pr}`2762`, pytest-benchmark {pr}"
