#: ../../../project/changelog.md:2165
msgid ""
"{{ Fix }} We now tell packagers (e.g., Webpack) to ignore npm-specific "
"imports when packing files for the browser. {pr}`2468`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../project/changelog.md:2169
msgid ""
"{{ Enhancement }} `run_in_pyodide` now has support for pytest assertion "
"rewriting and decorators such as `pytest.mark.parametrize` and hypothesis. "
"{pr}`2510`, {pr}`2541`"
